description: The SPDR Bloomberg 3-12 Month T-Bill ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the price and yield performance of the Bloomberg 3-12 Month U.S. Treasury Bill Index (the "Index")Seeks to provide exposure to publicly issued U.S. Treasury Bills that have remaining maturities between 3 and 12 monthsShort duration fixed income is less exposed to fluctuations in interest rates than longer duration securitiesRebalanced on the last business day of the month
name: SPDR Bloomberg 3-12 Month T-Bill ETF
